103
00:08:51,740 --> 00:08:57,120
I just hope our families can work together to get through this disaster,

104
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:59,719
instead of ending up in a lose-lose situation.

105
00:08:59,719 --> 00:09:05,839
To that end, you and I are in this together.

106
00:09:05,839 --> 00:09:09,160
So, Dongyang, you still care about my family, huh?

107
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:15,079
I thought you were putting me and my family at risk so you could be with Zhou Xiaoqing.

108
00:09:16,599 --> 00:09:19,360
So, you're upset because of her?

109
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,880
She's been with you for so long.

110
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:26,839
Haven't you thought about being with her for real?

111
00:09:26,839 --> 00:09:31,099
How can she ever compare to you?

112
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:44,779
I'm tired. I won't see you out.

113
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:54,539
Jiang Yingxian, you're really testing the limits of my gentlemanly patience.

114
00:09:57,079 --> 00:10:01,520
 I thought it'd be easier to break off the engagement by teaming up with Zhou Xiaoqing. 

115
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:13,020
